7. Cigar:pall-mall == Color:lilac
8. Beverage:fanta is in the middle
9. Nationality:german is on the far left
10. Cigar:dunhill is on the left or right of Pet:snake
11. Cigar:pall-mall is to the left or right of Pet:fish
12. Cigar:havana == Beverage:iced-tea
13. Nationality:pakistani == Cigar:cain
14. Nationality:german is to the left or right of Color:azure

